```plantuml
@startuml Cpanchal1_Chatbot101-with-AWS-Lambda
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor WebexUser

rectangle "Webex Teams" as WebexTeams #lightyellow {
  rectangle "Webhook" as Webhook #lightgoldenrodyellow
}

rectangle "AWS" as AWS #lightblue {
  rectangle "API Gateway" as APIGateway #aliceblue
  rectangle "Lambda Function" as LambdaFunction #lightsteelblue
}

rectangle "External API" as ExternalAPI #lightpink {
  rectangle "icanhazdadjoke.com" as JokeAPI #mistyrose
}

' ========== Connections ==========
WebexUser --> WebexTeams : mention bot to trigger

WebexTeams --> Webhook : trigger webhook on mention
Webhook --> APIGateway : send request to API Gateway
APIGateway --> LambdaFunction : invoke Lambda function

LambdaFunction --> JokeAPI : HTTP GET request for joke
JokeAPI --> LambdaFunction : return joke as JSON

LambdaFunction --> WebexTeams : post joke to room via Webex API

@enduml
```